{"tid":1386572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭至此小疑惑 求集思廣益","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T20:11:46.000Z","uid":293887,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6a711e0446673d753186183ccc1e465f92fd9270","tid":1386572,"uid":293887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:14:26.000Z","msg":"抗爭至此心中萌起小疑惑<br />\n<br />\n到底我地既<strong>目的</strong>係咩？<br />\n每次抗爭大家都疲於奔命，都會有人犧牲，無論被捕、受傷、付出都好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。但我們得到的又有多少？我們明白係連登出呢個post會俾人話係鬼、話分化撚。我都想係鬼，咁我就可以即刻自盡成為民主女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但好可惜咁多次，我地都係最前線，受傷既受傷、被捕既被捕，每次都損手爛腳地回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我地開始唔知道咁樣係咪正常⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n例如上環有49個兄弟被捕，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有45個以暴動罪起訴</strong>，用呢班小朋友既前途，我地交換左d咩返黎？</span><br />\n<br />\n自己企係前線，好明白當下其實已經無哂時間觀念，只能全心全意諗緊點樣對付眼前既敵人、點樣保護身邊既人、點樣幫後排buy time，一絲既猶疑足以落錯決定害死人。到左可以稍稍抖啖氣既呢個時候，我地有無機會諗一諗之後點行落去？每一次預告&gt;對家佈防&gt;到場建防線&gt;死守防線消耗人力物資&gt;圍攻而後撤，我地會唔會進化到更有效既方法？香港人除左愛心同銀包泛濫，最叻係咩呀？係進化啊！！！<br />\n<br />\n大家都逐漸明白，落左場，未必一定要打生打死才叫有付出，唔同崗位、唔同付出、唔同行動都有一定既作用。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">我地，只係非常唔想見到無謂既犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n如果犧牲有用，我承諾第一個把人頭雙手奉上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span><br />\n<br />\n無大台最大既好處就係可以二百萬個腦一齊諗，喇，集思廣益拋下磚先<br />\n個個星期六日都玩咁大實在會勞民傷財，如果可以軟硬兼施既，例如一星期不合作，一星期打，咁起碼可以過下冷河？又或者打突擊／游擊？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家點睇？</span></span>"},{"pid":"60ed7eab546d13be54a805ac3588d9bacf8607f3","tid":1386572,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:23:40.000Z","msg":"焦土 遍地開花"},{"pid":"2fe1547b84334e34132804e6ea1864ab9d7c1bf0","tid":1386572,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d9c03bf539b3857e61f6d4dc6ee3e42c0561a1","tid":1386572,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e8bc6413e2e49c9a179267b1e745077f722270e","tid":1386572,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb9b4ce3f6e794b1be71a6f788ad493b53536207","tid":1386572,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:25:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1e802210bb35ff90adf741d1ae79efa1098c207","tid":1386572,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:25:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed1e5b3fb9cac0b5ddd012430392d1ad79478b0b","tid":1386572,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:26:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0347cf96186c2cb56f9443d602100582bf0b6a48","tid":1386572,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:26:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2777a8c83d7bbcff77856b9a255b15d2a049433","tid":1386572,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:26:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cef32941f4c5479b5f11ede829eab57969ed93e7","tid":1386572,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:26:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26de486639831030377941ae8a35f20f11e983fe","tid":1386572,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:27:18.000Z","msg":"屌呀 又係吹水台 點推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e52a602e0e817740b8eb7007ea0d9a931e2c92","tid":1386572,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:27:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0dbb87ca78c96103885732e948242978bdd776a9","tid":1386572,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"